[ ] 8. DEPLOY TO RENDER
    a. Push Model 2/Build/ to a new GitHub repository
    b. Create new Web Service on Render
    c. Root directory: server
    d. Build command: npm install
    e. Start command: node server.js
    f. Add environment variables:
       - DATABASE_URL (your Supabase connection string)
